    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/868b772bd846a28e7c1f35d131a57f87.poster.avif?t=1769137569\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/868b772bd846a28e7c1f35d131a57f87.webm?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/868b772bd846a28e7c1f35d131a57f87.mp4?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/8dbe2d2169a74a19273503a20bad4ae2.poster.avif?t=1769137569\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/8dbe2d2169a74a19273503a20bad4ae2.webm?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/8dbe2d2169a74a19273503a20bad4ae2.mp4?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MEAT-GRINDER是一部视觉小说，讲述了一个名为Obi的女性职业杀手的人生。因为某种基因异常，她看着就像个18岁的花季少女。在她的旅途中，也总还能撞见些令人印象深刻的有趣角色。<br>在这个小演示版本中，你将不得不解决主角的急性财务问题，并帮助她的家人不要饿死！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/322b0e6c302d11a98b2466a0acaae870.avif?t=1769137569\" width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/841f884e44a4f772fc13ba0f1517bf8a.poster.avif?t=1769137569\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/841f884e44a4f772fc13ba0f1517bf8a.webm?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/841f884e44a4f772fc13ba0f1517bf8a.mp4?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在演示中，第一个小任务可用，这太容易了，不可能失败！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你将有一个短暂但有趣的冒险二十分钟没有重要的决定和结局，只是有一个好时机！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你还会结识一些情节的重要人物：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/5415cafa5977578038267d1cb80485d8.avif?t=1769137569\" width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kate</strong>：天才女孩。但是，很不幸，她的手臂被炮弹炸断了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/a389bc9adae1b44079a638d476736063.avif?t=1769137569\" width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Betty</strong>：（她总是躲在纸箱子里，这样你就看不见她那毁伤得不成人形的身体了。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/87052ee778070f1f78ec98509cecf244.avif?t=1769137569\" width=1560 height=874 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adolf</strong>：一个素质很差，很差，特别差的人工智能。负责给杀手和客户当中间人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Benya</strong>：一只猫。就真的只是一只猫。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/75024c2be64a4eeb67ce7bbf3bcdea78.poster.avif?t=1769137569\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/75024c2be64a4eeb67ce7bbf3bcdea78.webm?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/75024c2be64a4eeb67ce7bbf3bcdea78.mp4?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个短暂的任务中，Obi试图杀死一个糟糕的建筑公司的董事，但一切都没有按计划进行。..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-特立独行，摄人心魄的美术风格！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-原创的OST！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-一大堆会把你功德扣光光的黑色幽默！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/2d66c5b9711a4ffc85c1d9a80536c55d.poster.avif?t=1769137569\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/2d66c5b9711a4ffc85c1d9a80536c55d.webm?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240730/extras/2d66c5b9711a4ffc85c1d9a80536c55d.mp4?t=1769137569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
